<br />
Just to give you a rough estimate of my gear 1300 ac, 4900 hp, 20 worn atk, 100+ in all resists, primal, 61% self haste, a GSo4W and i do have 7k HT.<br />
<br />
If anybody has soloed her post revamp can you let me know here or PM?  I would get people to help but shes been spawining at weird times and people arent on =\</div>
