		<div>I have about the same gear/stats as you, yet I don't really think I could 2-box her.  I've killed her by 2-boxing with a cleric MANY times since the revamp and I always imagined it would be too hard for me to solo.  It's possible, but I would guess unlikely.<br />
<br />
One thing I do think I can explain though is why you think her guards are tied to her.  They aren't.  If you are looking into her room, there are 2 golems on the left, 2 golems on the right, and she is in the center.  However, there is a roaming undead mob that walks along the right side of the room, behind the golems.  This is in addition to the 2 roamers that path all the way through her room and the hallway that precedes it, which of course you have to kill first.  Since he's not a static mob, you probably still had aggro on the roamer while you had snare/fd pulled drusella.  And of course the undead roamer will bring the golems in the room with him.  So I guess you should kill that roamer as well (unless for some reason you can use our undead pacify on him... I think he's much too high for it to stick though)<br />
<br />
Anyway, late response, but hopefully useful to somebody....</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
